title: AHS 1984 Episode 2 Review & Synopsis
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Hey everyone. Sorry the video was late, but it was my daughter's 13th birthday last week. I decided to celebrate her day instead of making a review for AHS. Thanks for your patience and comments.
Jonas Shevoore is an anagram for Jason Voorhees. Could this be a hint that Jonas' mother is possibly a killer?
why is nobody talking about Xavier's tape being called the X-Man Cometh
Montana yelling "yeah we all f-ing know!!!" made me laugh so hard!

My new theory is maybe Margaret and Mr. Jingles were partners before. Other counselors found Margaret's extreme religiousness too annoying. Mr. Jingles were somewhat kinda "bullied". And so saying that, the two planned the massacre. But Margaret betrayed Mr. Jingles and put all the blame on him, and so he later ended in the asylum.
